name: Stackwise
long_description:
The open source AI app boilerplate collection, ranging from music and audio generation, to streaming and image descriptions.

We are fully open source - star us at https://github.com/stackwiseai/stackwise. If you're interesting in contributing, we'd be happy to help you get started!

We have backgrounds working on agentic behaviour and generative AI. We met through AutoGPT where we were both lead maintainers and then founding ai engineers. Here, we built the go-to benchmark in the agent space, and published a NeurIPS paper together.
one_liner: The open source AI app collection
